<div style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left;">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Subscription Confirmation</h2>
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p>We are pleased to confirm that your subscription to <strong>{{subscriptionName}}</strong> has been successfully activated. Below are the details of your subscription:</p>
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
            <tr>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f8f8f8;">Subscription Name</th>
                <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">{{subscriptionName}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f8f8f8;">Starts At</th>
                <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">{{startsAt}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f8f8f8;">Expires At</th>
                <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">{{expires}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f8f8f8;">Trial Starts</th>
                <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">{{trialStarts}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f8f8f8;">Trial Ends</th>
                <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">{{trialEnds}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <p>We are committed to providing you with the highest level of service. If you have any questions or require further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>Eislett Team</p>
    </div>
</div>
